Dalber pendant lamp My Little Jungle

Brighten up your kids room with this super cute hanging lamp. On the lampshade are several cute animals. When you switch off the lamp the animals give a beautiful glow in the dark light.

Colour: multicolour
Material: plastic
Gender: junior
Dimensions: 25 x 26 cm (L x W)
Lighting: E27 (not included)
Power: max. 60W

Material: Kunststoff
